>
> I like them, I just wish Ornn had specific quotes for his allies when they upgraded specific items.
> 
> {{item:3071}} - &quot;Noxian axes are good. Obsidian makes it better.&quot;
> 
> {{item:3068}} - &quot;Hand it over. Just needs a bit more time in the forge.&quot;
> 
> {{item:3001}} - &quot;I don&#x27;t like magic. But I&#x27;ll make it tougher for you, I suppose.&quot;
> 
> {{item:3190}} - &quot;That looks dumb around your neck. Let&#x27;s put it on your head.&quot;

I know! Unfortunately, our VO pipeline is locked way before the kit is finalized due to our localization process. This is something that would have been implemented if we could have. Who knows, if Ornn ever gets a legendary and we have the actor right there....
